WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love In A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.150
=Episode 5=

00:01:09.640 --> 00:01:12.400
(So you told me to conceal my edge)

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.160
(in order to protect me.)

00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:16.320
(So the place you lived in)

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:17.520
(was hell as well.)

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:20.120
(But the enemy of an enemy is a friend.)

00:01:20.120 --> 00:01:22.760
(Since he harbors ulterior motives
toward the Lu family too,)

00:01:22.760 --> 00:01:24.560
(we should side with each other.)

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.320
(What do you think, elder sister?)

00:01:40.660 --> 00:01:41.600
What are you doing here?

00:01:43.480 --> 00:01:44.720
I'm here to reconcile with you.

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:46.320
Reconcile with me?

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:49.800
Didn't you say that I misunderstood you?

00:01:50.500 --> 00:01:52.120
That's why I'm here to apologize to you.

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:56.120
Lu, I never expected you

00:01:56.960 --> 00:01:58.120
to be this civil with me.

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:00.040
What?

00:02:00.720 --> 00:02:01.690
Are you not used to it?

00:02:05.360 --> 00:02:06.080
That's not it.

00:02:06.390 --> 00:02:07.280
I'm very used to it.

00:02:11.880 --> 00:02:13.320
Why are you trying to join Lu Group?

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:18.920
I need to make money

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:22.480
to pay off my father's debt.

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:28.290
I can split half of
the Lu family's wealth with you.

00:02:31.720 --> 00:02:32.840
What did you say?

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:34.720
I said,

00:02:36.440 --> 00:02:37.320
I can split half of

00:02:37.320 --> 00:02:38.840
the Lu family's wealth with you.

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:41.360
However, I will take
all the inheritances.

00:02:44.620 --> 00:02:46.870
Have you always been
this straightforward all your life?

00:02:47.690 --> 00:02:49.240
Since I'm here to reconcile with you,

00:02:50.080 --> 00:02:51.640
there's no need to beat around the bush.

00:02:52.790 --> 00:02:54.360
I could never wrap my head around this.

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:56.890
You're the only daughter
of the Lu family.

00:02:57.200 --> 00:02:58.720
Why do you care about money so much?

00:02:59.090 --> 00:03:01.200
Aren't you inheriting
all of the inheritances anyway?

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:02.560
Now that you're back,

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:04.520
no one can say for sure,

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:06.240
Elder brother.

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:09.480
Don't worry.

00:03:10.040 --> 00:03:11.160
You won't miss a single thing

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:13.240
you desire.

00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:15.760
It's a deal, then.

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:31.040
Can you drink?

00:03:39.320 --> 00:03:40.160
Man.

00:03:42.040 --> 00:03:42.880
Man?

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:47.880
Man?

00:03:50.360 --> 00:03:51.160
Man.

00:03:51.160 --> 00:03:51.800
Yes?

00:03:52.640 --> 00:03:53.080
Mom.

00:03:53.700 --> 00:03:55.640
We're going to visit
Mr. Shu and the rest today.

00:03:55.640 --> 00:03:56.680
Get ready.

00:03:56.680 --> 00:03:57.680
I'll be ready after my shower.

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:58.200
Okay.

00:04:22.840 --> 00:04:24.240
This bed is so comfortable.

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:26.400
You do take after your mother.

00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:28.520
Hurry and tidy up.

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:29.820
Don't let my mother see you here.

00:04:34.520 --> 00:04:35.400
Man,

00:04:35.400 --> 00:04:37.000
Jiajia gave me a scarf last time.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.390
I want to give her something in return.

00:04:46.500 --> 00:04:48.040
What are you doing in my son's room?

00:04:50.520 --> 00:04:51.400
Isn't it obvious?

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:56.000
Do you think you can take your revenge

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:57.160
by getting close to my son?

00:04:57.160 --> 00:04:58.240
Oh?

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:04.240
So I can take my revenge by
just getting close to your son?

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:07.640
Come with me.

00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:09.080
Let go!

00:05:09.080 --> 00:05:10.640
You don't tell me what to do.

00:05:10.640 --> 00:05:11.640
I don't tell you what to do?

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:12.560
I'm your mother now.

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:14.040
Why can't I tell you what to do?

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:16.240
You're not my mother.

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:17.840
You don't have the right
to tell me what to do!

00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:19.280
Who said so?

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:23.040
Lu?

00:05:25.520 --> 00:05:26.240
Mom?

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:27.880
My parents never hit me

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:30.720
in my entire life before.

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:32.440
Lu?

00:05:32.440 --> 00:05:34.080
Let go!

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:34.760
Man,

00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:35.440
let her go!

00:05:35.440 --> 00:05:36.520
Let her clarify herself.

00:05:36.520 --> 00:05:37.320
Mom, you should leave first.

00:05:37.320 --> 00:05:38.590
I'll clarify the situation later.

00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:45.240
Calm down!

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:47.560
She was the one who stole
everything from me.

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:48.880
What gives her the right to do so?

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:53.280
Alright now.

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.080
Calm down.

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:59.840
You can't resolve any issues
by being impulsive.

00:06:01.040 --> 00:06:02.760
How else can I resolve my issues, then?

00:06:18.320 --> 00:06:19.080
You!

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:41.880
Stop filming me!

00:06:42.640 --> 00:06:44.040
I told you already. Stop.

00:06:47.840 --> 00:06:48.880
How's your hand?

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:50.960
Like that.

00:06:50.960 --> 00:06:52.360
I won't die from it.

00:06:54.760 --> 00:06:56.000
Sometimes,

00:06:56.800 --> 00:06:58.520
everything isn't black or white.

00:06:58.520 --> 00:07:00.480
Sometimes the middle ground

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:02.120
is the best solution.

00:07:03.440 --> 00:07:04.320
You're too ferocious.

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:06.760
You're just like
a bucking horse without a leash.

00:07:10.037 --> 00:07:10.990
Stay out of my business.

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:15.920
If I don't mind your business, who will?

00:07:16.412 --> 00:07:19.052
I told you already.
I don't need an elder brother.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:22.000
What do you need, then?

00:07:23.160 --> 00:07:24.480
I'll stop here.

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:27.790
I have an equestrian lesson to take.

00:07:28.920 --> 00:07:29.880
Turn around.

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:31.600
Don't film me!

00:07:39.240 --> 00:07:41.160
Lu Zhu, what a coincidence.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:44.400
Ms. Shu, are you here for a lesson too?

00:07:44.400 --> 00:07:46.880
Yeah. My horsemanship isn't that good.

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:49.860
I'm not sure if I'll be able to play
in the fall membership tournament yet.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.600
By the way, where's your elder brother?

00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:52.840
I don't know.

00:07:53.112 --> 00:07:54.912
Does he have a girlfriend?

00:07:55.080 --> 00:07:56.040
I don't know.

00:07:56.487 --> 00:07:58.087
Let me ask you something.

00:07:58.087 --> 00:08:00.207
Do you think I'm a good fit for him?

00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:04.360
You have to ask him that question.

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:05.280
How would I know?

00:08:05.725 --> 00:08:06.812
You have a point.

00:08:06.812 --> 00:08:09.052
But we've been getting along
for the past few days.

00:08:09.060 --> 00:08:11.800
I plan to confess to him at the
Youth Entrepreneurship Association party

00:08:11.812 --> 00:08:12.612
tonight.

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:14.760
I wish you success.

00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:17.480
Ms. Shu, I remembered
that I had something to do.

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:18.320
I'll make a move first.

00:08:18.320 --> 00:08:19.240
Okay.

00:08:21.200 --> 00:08:24.480
Qun, where's the address for the Youth
Entrepreneurship Association party?

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:27.440
Send it to me. I'll be attending too.

00:08:33.880 --> 00:08:35.240
Isn't that Lu Zhu?

00:08:36.160 --> 00:08:38.040
She's so gorgeous today.

00:08:38.040 --> 00:08:39.400
She's quite popular, huh?

00:08:52.960 --> 00:08:54.680
She's here to have some fun.

00:08:54.680 --> 00:08:57.480
You shouldn't bother her.

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:05.680
Ye Man,

00:09:05.680 --> 00:09:06.960
I like you.

00:09:07.640 --> 00:09:10.360
I fell for you at first sight.

00:09:15.240 --> 00:09:16.280
I'm sorry.

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:21.160
Cheers.

00:09:38.920 --> 00:09:41.360
That day, you told me
that you didn't need an elder brother.

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:44.240
What do you need, then?

00:09:52.087 --> 00:09:53.625
What are you doing?

00:09:53.625 --> 00:09:55.145
Someone will see us, you know?

00:09:57.800 --> 00:09:59.600
So what?

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.760
What are you doing here today?

00:10:01.760 --> 00:10:03.200
Are you here to find new prey?

00:10:04.080 --> 00:10:04.880
Ye Man.

00:10:05.520 --> 00:10:06.600
Call me elder brother.

00:10:08.880 --> 00:10:09.680
No way.

00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:31.000
Let me bite your ears off
if you can't hear with them.

00:10:52.237 --> 00:10:56.737
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:10:56.962 --> 00:11:00.750
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:11:00.925 --> 00:11:05.000
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:09.137
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:11:09.262 --> 00:11:13.037
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:11:13.037 --> 00:11:16.812
♪I'll learn to stop
longing for what's gone♪

00:11:16.812 --> 00:11:19.087
♪The you in my memories♪

00:11:19.087 --> 00:11:21.100
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:11:21.100 --> 00:11:26.537
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:11:28.100 --> 00:11:33.537
♪Forget you completely♪